Package emissary.util.shell

Class TempFileNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • emissary.util.shell.TempFileNames
  • public class TempFileNames
extends Object
    A related set file and directory path names suitable for operations that require temporary disk-backed files. The names do not directly imply that corresponding files and directories actually exist; I/O operations including creating or deletions of files or directories is the responsibility of TempFileNames instance consumers.
